{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think there are 17 [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this is Budapest, basically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's far out to the east.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Reel number two, tape number two, with Leslie Aigner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, in Csepel, we lived in a-- a duplex.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a-- it was basically a three-room duplex.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A small front room, very small, and a great room, which was the bedroom, and a very small kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have no-- we had running water, but no bathroom of-- such as shower.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we used tubs inside to clean ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- for five of us, it was pretty crowded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because all five of us lived-- slept in one room, in the biggest room in the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so, this-- this is where I arrived in 1943, and this is where I started my trade school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and my father was inducted, and my sister had to go into the factory, only three of us were left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to move into the ghetto area, which was a similar situation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a house with two apartments, but it was a garden in the house, and that's where those pictures were taken.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't even hardly packed, unpacked when we got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because in the ghetto, we lived maybe less-- about a month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Approximately a month.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we were taken to-- the Hungarian Nazi at Arrow Cross ordered us to pack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were taken to Budakalasz, which was-- which had an abandoned big factory which they didn't use any more-- outdated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were barbed wire around the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they collected from the outskirts of Budapest, not from Budapest, because Budapest had the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And from the outskirts of Budapest, they gathered the small community Jews over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had 3,000, 4,000 together.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
